	<content><![CDATA[const castArray = val => (Array.isArray(val) ? val : [val]);]]></content>
	<description>Casts the provided value as an array if it's not one.  Use `Array.isArray()` to determine if `val` is an array and return it as-is or encapsulated in an array accordingly.</description>
